stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> running: registerAgentForeground\n（创建任务 + 注册到 AppState）
    running --> backgrounded: backgroundAgentTask\n（isBackgrounded=true，Background Signal 触发）
    running --> completed: 正常完成
    running --> failed: 执行错误
    running --> killed: killAsyncAgent\n（AbortController.abort）
    backgrounded --> completed: 后台正常完成
    backgrounded --> failed: 后台执行错误
    backgrounded --> killed: killAllRunningAgentTasks
    completed --> [*]: evictAfter 到期 + retain=false
    failed --> [*]: evictAfter 到期 + retain=false
    killed --> [*]: evictAfter 到期 + retain=false
